# Cursor Rules for EDC Companion

## GitHub Integration
- This project is connected to GitHub: https://github.com/grakozy/every-day-carry-demo
- When reviewing pull requests, fetch PR comments and reviews using GitHub CLI
- Apply suggested changes from code reviews when appropriate
- Make updates directly to the codebase based on review feedback

## Code Review Workflow
- When asked to review PR feedback, use `gh pr view` and `gh pr view --comments` to get review details
- Apply fixes suggested in PR reviews
- Commit changes with descriptive messages referencing the PR review

